	"description": "Today we&#x27;re lucky to have almost endless resources at our fingertips for\nlearning web development. Among these resources are coding games. \n\nI&#x27;ve created games like Flexbox Froggy\n[https://codepip.com/games/flexbox-froggy/] and Grid Garden\n[https://codepip.com/games/flexbox-froggy/], along with others like CSS Diner\n[https://flukeout.github.io/] and CodeCombat [https://codecombat.com/], that\nhelp package an educational experience into a fun, engaging format.\n\nYet, as with any learning resource, ",
